The paper deals with image processing and machine learning techniques to identify table structures in documents. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves natural language processing techniques to extract information from unstructured documents, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.CL (Computation and Language). The use of generative adversarial networks and optimization algorithms suggests a focus on machine learning, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.DL (Deep Learning).
